name: REFRACT - The GIFs - GIF-r37/48
description:
GIF 37 of 48.

This GIF is part of C7 along with GIF-r34, GIF-r35 and GIF-r36. First 11 collectors to complete C7 will be awarded with 1 edition of OBJKT#XXXXXX (to be revealed on Oct 7th).

First 11 collectors to complete the serie will be awarded with 1 edition of REFRACT -AV- (to be revealed on Oct 8th). 

Items from this collection will be minted and swaped once a day from Aug 20th to Oct 6th.

576x360px; 39f@30fps; 3,85Mb. 3ds Max, After Effects, Premiere.
